padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;\">·<span style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"RU\" style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">Выполняйте</span><span style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"RU\" style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">массаж дренажной щёткой</span><span style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"RU\" style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">до принятия душа, на сухую кожу. Начните</span><span style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"RU\" style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">массаж с ног, постепенно поднимаясь выше. Круговыми движениями обработайте</span><span style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"RU\" style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">бедра и ягодицы.&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"RU\" style=\"background-repeat: initial; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Будьте внимательны к зонам, где расположены лимфоузлы (пах, подмышечные впадины), а также к зоне декольте и шеи.</span><span lang=\"RU\" style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp;В завершение</span><span style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"RU\" style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">процедуры помассируйте</span><span style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"RU\" style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">руки и плечи легкими скользящими движениями. После сухого массажа необходимо принять прохладный душ, чтобы смыть частички эпидермиса и охладить кожу.</span><span lang=\"RU\" style=\"background-repeat: initial; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;Рекомендуется начать массаж с 3-х минут и каждый день увеличивать время процедуры, чтобы кожа привыкла к новым ощущениям. Для достижения наилучшего эффекта необходимо проводить процедуру массажа регулярно. После массажа увлажнить кожу кремом.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-repeat: initial; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 36pt; font-family: Manrope, sans-serif; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 16px; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"RU\" style=\"background-repeat: initial; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><br style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><u style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: inherit;\">Выполнять массаж сухой щеткой рекомендуется не более двух раз в неделю.</u></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-repeat: initial; box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 36pt